* SOLO TELEOP *
///////////////////// GAMEPAD 1: //////////////////////

* Left Joystick X and Y - strafe (field-centric)
* Right Joystick X - turn (drive)

* Left Trigger - prep to grab clip off wall, then grab and prep score clip on release

* Right Trigger - 100% extension intaking
* Right Bumper - high bucket prep

* Left Bumper - deposit bucket or clip, and general purpose scoring arm and vert slides reset

* //A - slam clip moved
* B - also high bucket prep
* //X - prep to grab clip off wall
* //Y - grab and prep score clip

* D-Pad Right - rotate intake claw right
* D-Pad Left - rotate intake claw left
* D-Pad Down - auto intake claw orient (camera)

///////////////////// GAMEPAD 2: //////////////////////

* Left Joystick Y - L2 hang manual control

* Left Bumper - drop sample behind robot and return
* X - transfer, then prep to drop sample behind robot
* Y - navx reset

* Left Trigger - rotate intake claw left
* Right Trigger - rotate intake claw right

